{"tid":404970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【回應何君堯「殺無赦」言論　袁國強指不可單憑字句判斷是否違法】","createTime":"2017-09-18T13:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T16:54:36.000Z","uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7323300af9a510df1e0042f267cab92a929d5825","tid":404970,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"建制派立法會議員何君堯昨日發起「反港獨」集會期間，揚言要對支持港獨人士「殺無赦」，涉嫌作出恐嚇言論<br />\n<br />\n律政司司長袁國強今日回應時則表示，不可單憑個別字句去判斷是否構成刑事罪行，要從整體去衡量，包括要考慮字句和背景。<br />\n<br />\n袁國強又指，如有任何人認有需要跟進，可以依照一貫程序處理。<br />\n<br />\n此外，袁又重申，「港獨」不符香港憲制及法律地位，鼓吹港獨對香港沒有任何好處，聚焦其他問題會對香港更有建設性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28aa7fe2e3cff8fd385c8b1348bef5b9b1e7db86","tid":404970,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:21:36.000Z","msg":"噉港獨兩隻字又話犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5acd94ca94bb92015ff38800387199000aee08ce","tid":404970,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac8a7d035a482121bd6af50b21a16187d8d89557","tid":404970,"uid":26030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:22:53.000Z","msg":"咁重奪個奪字呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658ec92e97a2371680352494aa92ab8047056c8e","tid":404970,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:23:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6edf231a4e2c970736b8422a472a84fc6c59b61b","tid":404970,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/212544_8e4ca09232b39063213a33035c1d072f.jpg\" data-t